Question-2
Write a java program to encrypt a grade  by adding 8 to it. Decrypt it to Show the correct grade 
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        char grade = 'B';
        grade = (char) (grade + 8);
        System.out.println(grade);
        //decrypt
        grade = (char) (grade - 8);
        System.out.println(grade);
    }
}
Output:
J
B

